# Supplier Communication Templates

**Purpose:** Standardized templates for communicating with suppliers and manufacturers

**Owner:** @DesignEng, @SeniorEng  
**Version:** 1.0  
**Date:** 2024-12-22

---

## 1. Request for Quote (RFQ) Template

**Subject:** Request for Quote - [Part Number] - [Part Name]

**Date:** [Date]  
**Project:** [Project Name]  
**Part Number:** [Part Number]  
**Part Name:** [Part Name]  
**Quantity:** [Quantity]  
**Target Delivery:** [Date]

**Dear [Supplier Name],**

We are requesting a quote for the manufacture of the following part:

**Part Information:**
- Part Number: [Part Number]
- Part Name: [Part Name]
- Material: [Material Specification]
- Quantity: [Quantity]
- Target Delivery Date: [Date]

**Attachments:**
- Technical Drawing: [Part Number]_drawing.pdf
- 3D Model: [Part Number].step
- Manufacturing Notes: [Part Number]_notes.md
- BOM (if applicable): [BOM file]

**Requirements:**
- [ ] All dimensions per technical drawing
- [ ] Tolerances per ASME Y14.5 standard
- [ ] Surface finish per specifications
- [ ] Material certification required
- [ ] First Article Inspection (FAI) required
- [ ] Quality documentation required

**Please provide:**
1. Unit price
2. Setup cost (if applicable)
3. Lead time
4. Minimum order quantity (MOQ)
5. Payment terms
6. Quality certifications

**Questions or clarifications:**
Please contact [Name] at [Email] or [Phone]

Thank you for your time and consideration.

**Best regards,**  
[Your Name]  
[Company Name]

---

## 2. Technical Specification Package Template

**Subject:** Technical Specification Package - [Part Number]

**Date:** [Date]  
**Project:** [Project Name]  
**Part Number:** [Part Number]

**Package Contents:**
1. Technical Drawing (PDF, DXF, DWG)
2. 3D Model (STEP file with PMI)
3. Manufacturing Notes
4. Material Specifications
5. Quality Requirements
6. Inspection Procedures

**Part Specifications:**
- Part Number: [Part Number]
- Part Name: [Part Name]
- Material: [Material Specification]
- Revision: [Revision]

**Critical Dimensions:**
[List critical dimensions with tolerances]

**GD&T Requirements:**
[List GD&T callouts]

**Surface Finish:**
[List surface finish requirements]

**Thread Specifications:**
[List thread specifications]

**Quality Requirements:**
- First Article Inspection (FAI) required
- Material certification required
- Inspection documentation required
- Compliance with [Standards]

**Delivery Requirements:**
- Packaging: [Packaging requirements]
- Labeling: [Labeling requirements]
- Documentation: [Documentation requirements]

**Contact Information:**
For questions or clarifications, contact:
- Technical: [Name] - [Email] - [Phone]
- Quality: [Name] - [Email] - [Phone]
- Procurement: [Name] - [Email] - [Phone]

