## 3. Change Notification Template

**Subject:** Engineering Change Notification - [Part Number] - [Change Description]

**Date:** [Date]  
**ECO Number:** [ECO-XXX]  
**Part Number:** [Part Number]  
**Revision:** [Old Revision] â†’ [New Revision]  
**Priority:** [High / Medium / Low]

**Dear [Supplier Name],**

This is to notify you of an engineering change to the above part number.

**Change Description:**
[Detailed description of the change]

**Reason for Change:**
[Reason for the change]

**Impact:**
- **Technical Impact:** [Description]
- **Cost Impact:** [Description]
- **Schedule Impact:** [Description]
- **Tooling Impact:** [Description]

**Effective Date:**
- Change effective: [Date]
- Last order with old revision: [Date]
- First order with new revision: [Date]

**Attachments:**
- Updated Technical Drawing: [Part Number]_drawing.pdf
- Updated 3D Model: [Part Number].step
- Change Summary: [Change summary document]

**Action Required:**
- [ ] Acknowledge receipt of change notification
- [ ] Confirm understanding of change
- [ ] Provide impact assessment (if requested)
- [ ] Update manufacturing processes
- [ ] Update quality procedures

**Questions:**
Please contact [Name] at [Email] or [Phone]

**Best regards,**  
[Your Name]  
[Company Name]

