**Delivery Schedule:**

| Part Number | Part Name | Quantity | Required Date | Status |
|-------------|-----------|----------|---------------|--------|
| [Part-001] | [Name] | [Qty] | [Date] | [Status] |
| [Part-002] | [Name] | [Qty] | [Date] | [Status] |

**Notes:**
- All deliveries must include:
  - Material certification
  - Inspection documentation
  - FAI report (for first delivery)
- Packaging requirements: [Requirements]
- Labeling requirements: [Requirements]

**Shipping Address:**
[Shipping address]

**Contact:**
For delivery questions, contact [Name] at [Email] or [Phone]

**Best regards,**  
[Your Name]  
[Company Name]

---

## Usage Notes

1. **Customize templates** for your specific needs
2. **Fill in all placeholders** before sending
3. **Attach required documents** (drawings, models, specifications)
4. **Keep records** of all communications
5. **Follow up** on responses and actions

